    title: "Estrada da Serra", location: "Serra Gaúcha, RS", coords: "29°10'S 51°10'W", category: "Moto"
  },
  {
    img: "https://d36hbw14aib5lz.cloudfront.net/310519663568009244/9oWeQAjFk7GoTWpFXegazj/natureza_cachoeira-8cc9uiv272ewBMWutpAmM3.webp?Expires=1807954677&Signature=kK9IQg6OzHkvCF~3BoySUjhwraS7TwXt9wYu79WuT3RQOFxC9eMZ-v46xujuQ0GJfEtSUtBQlQezswkDb74gLDex68M5U9RuXOLcqxkTCaIBjijJTEoc8jp7IBbF~IGXJRRcRqV~Jg3dxkVG-xsYmog5aZwW6g1eRF3oFwyD0mWY7lJm4KqDpF1jwkBwP3lTrKa9bYerV9MAFkLjMIHWP5fYXbv036zHZtk-SHUpu1DKsQm2ENzsOcxbpDEi8NapXTbllYDgPvdN0WvuUd~oZnTedacpimEAI500bw6NerOmflwhtGa90ysJmIBeDyZj3DABoBNs6eq8COFGtfk2dw__&Key-Pair-Id=K1MP89RTKNH4J",
